import React from 'react' import Title from '../components/Title' import { Dados } from '../components/Dados' import { useState } from 'react'; function Password() { const [cvc, setCvc] = useState(''); } function handleChange(event) { setCvc(event.target.value); } export const Cadastro = () => { return (
<Dados/> <div className='float-left'> Dados Pessoais <br /> <input type="text" placeholder='Nome' /> <br /> <input type="number" placeholder='Telefone' /> <br /> <input type="text" placeholder='Endereço'/> <br /><br /> Plano Escolhido <br /> <button>FREE</button> <button>PLUS</button> </div> <div> Dados do Cartão <br /> <input type="text" placeholder='Nome do cartão' /> <br /> <input type="number" maxLength="20" placeholder='Número do cartão' /> <div> <label htmlFor="cvc">CVC:</label> <input type="password" id="cvc" maxLength="3" pattern="[0-9]{3}" value={cvc} onChange={handleChange} /> </div> </div> </div> ) }
